      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普同意接受 FBI 关于枪击案调查的问询</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/trump-agrees-to-be-interviewed-by-fbi-in-shooter-investigation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普同意接受联邦调查局的采访，调查人员正在深入调查这起导致这位前总统受伤并引发政治风暴的暗杀事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/trump-agrees-to-be-interviewed-by-fbi-in-shooter-investigation</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 14:50:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国政府问责署称五角大楼抑制高超音速武器问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/pentagon-holding-back-on-hypersonic-weapons-troubles-gao-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国会审计人员称，五角大楼并未向国会和公众提供关于开发高超音速武器以对抗中国和俄罗斯已部署的高超音速武器所面临的困难和挑战的全面评估。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/pentagon-holding-back-on-hypersonic-weapons-troubles-gao-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 14:02:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列军队突袭关押加沙战争嫌疑犯的监狱，指控其涉嫌虐待</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/israeli-army-raids-jail-for-gaza-war-suspects-over-abuse-claims</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列军警称，在有指控称一名囚犯遭受“严重虐待”后，军警突袭了一座关押加沙战争囚犯的监狱，此举遭到总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡执政联盟部分成员的批评。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/israeli-army-raids-jail-for-gaza-war-suspects-over-abuse-claims</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 13:45:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
