      <title>梅洛尼发挥调解作用平衡欧盟与中国的关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/meloni-tells-xi-italy-can-broker-balanced-ties-between-eu-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼提出要促进中国与欧盟之间改善贸易关系，并呼吁习近平主席“平衡”欧盟与世界第二大经济体之间的贸易关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/meloni-tells-xi-italy-can-broker-balanced-ties-between-eu-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 10:52:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登呼吁对最高法院法官实施严格的新限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/joe-biden-wants-supreme-court-term-limits-changes-on-presidential-immunity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登将于周一呼吁立法者通过新的具有约束力的道德规则和最高法院法官的任期限制，这是一项将从根本上改变美国最高法院的全面提案的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/joe-biden-wants-supreme-court-term-limits-changes-on-presidential-immunity</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 09:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国敦促以色列保持冷静，以色列考虑对戈兰高地致命火箭弹袭击作出回应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/israel-weighs-response-to-deadly-golan-strike-as-us-urges-calm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在以色列占领的戈兰高地发生火箭弹袭击，造成十几名年轻人死亡后，美国和其他世界大国试图阻止以色列和真主党的冲突演变为全面战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/israel-weighs-response-to-deadly-golan-strike-as-us-urges-calm</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 07:57:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
